entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have destroyed all the canisters around Camp Beta.
entries.journal_entry_description: Find leaking Blackwing canisters around camp. Place the thermal detonators on the canister to destroy them.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: When you have met your collection quota, the job will be done.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Go back to camp and meet with your contact to collect the reward.
